cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with multilabel image annotation, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes the use of Deep Neural Networks, which falls under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of approximate top-k ranking objectives is related to information retrieval, which falls under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The NUS-WIDE dataset is a multimedia dataset, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). Finally, the use of Deep Neural Networks also falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
